WEBVTT

00:00:29.294 --> 00:00:30.623
To se zove hrabrost.

00:00:31.354 --> 00:00:33.037
I poput straha,

00:00:33.061 --> 00:00:34.443
hrabrost je zarazna.

00:00:35.870 --> 00:00:38.118
Ja sam iz East St. Louisa, Illinois.

00:00:38.143 --> 00:00:39.302
To je mali grad

00:00:39.327 --> 00:00:42.141
uz rijeku Mississippi,
St. Louis, Missouri.

00:00:42.165 --> 00:00:46.238
Cijeli sam život živio u i oko St. Louisa.

00:00:48.443 --> 00:00:49.777
Kada je Michaela Browna,

00:00:49.777 --> 00:00:51.023
običnog tinejdžera,

00:00:51.047 --> 00:00:55.597
ustrijelila policija 2014.
u Fergusonu, Missouri,

00:00:55.621 --> 00:00:58.780
još jednom predgrađu,
no sjeverno od St. Louisa,

00:00:58.804 --> 00:01:00.337
sjećam se da sam pomislio